00:38:43,760 --> 00:38:44,760
Come on.

589
00:38:45,600 --> 00:38:46,880
Take him back.

590
00:39:00,400 --> 00:39:01,000
Mr. Gu,

591
00:39:01,160 --> 00:39:02,760
Miss Dong is waiting for you.

592
00:39:12,480 --> 00:39:13,680
I'm sorry, Miss Dong.

593
00:39:14,240 --> 00:39:15,720
I picked up a friend at the train station.

594
00:39:15,720 --> 00:39:16,580
Sorry I'm late.

595
00:39:17,480 --> 00:39:19,140
This is my friend, Qu Manting,

596
00:39:19,320 --> 00:39:20,120
a famous star.

597
00:39:21,200 --> 00:39:21,730
Manting,

598
00:39:22,160 --> 00:39:23,160
this is Miss Dong,

599
00:39:23,320 --> 00:39:24,760
my fiancée.

600
00:39:25,200 --> 00:39:25,960
Miss Dong.

601
00:39:26,160 --> 00:39:27,680
I've heard so much about you.

602
00:39:27,680 --> 00:39:28,880
You're so beautiful.

603
00:39:30,880 --> 00:39:31,810
Nice to meet you.

604
00:39:32,480 --> 00:39:33,160
Take a seat.

605
00:39:35,000 --> 00:39:35,600
Come here.

606
00:39:37,680 --> 00:39:38,440
Thanks.

607
00:39:46,360 --> 00:39:47,480
I asked someone to book

608
00:39:47,480 --> 00:39:49,610
a table in this restaurant yesterday.

609
00:39:49,720 --> 00:39:50,720
I told you before.

610
00:39:50,760 --> 00:39:52,320
The steak here is delicious.

611
00:39:52,320 --> 00:39:53,440
You'll like it.

612
00:39:54,160 --> 00:39:55,120
As long as it's your choice,

613
00:39:55,120 --> 00:39:56,000
I like it.

614
00:39:57,960 --> 00:39:59,480
Ms. Qu is a singer.

615
00:40:00,200 --> 00:40:00,720
Yeah.

616
00:40:01,240 --> 00:40:03,240
Then you must be familiar

617
00:40:03,240 --> 00:40:04,400
with clubs?

618
00:40:04,760 --> 00:40:06,020
If you're interested,

619
00:40:06,240 --> 00:40:08,170
Yanzhen can take you there for fun.

620
00:40:08,600 --> 00:40:09,800
He's a regular guest.

621
00:40:09,880 --> 00:40:11,120
We met there.

622
00:40:13,960 --> 00:40:16,480
I've received western education since I was young.

623
00:40:16,480 --> 00:40:18,760
But my parents are traditional people.

624
00:40:19,480 --> 00:40:21,480
They won't allow me to get in

625
00:40:21,960 --> 00:40:23,360
places like clubs.

626
00:40:23,920 --> 00:40:25,080
After all, we girls

627
00:40:25,720 --> 00:40:27,180
should behave ourselves.

628
00:40:28,240 --> 00:40:29,700
In such places like a club,

629
00:40:30,240 --> 00:40:31,570
however famous you are,

630
00:40:32,200 --> 00:40:34,240
you'll be despised by people.

631
00:40:34,640 --> 00:40:35,370
You think so?

632
00:40:35,720 --> 00:40:36,680
What a pity!

633
00:40:37,240 --> 00:40:38,240
I was planning to

634
00:40:38,240 --> 00:40:39,720
go to a club with Yanzhen.

635
00:40:40,080 --> 00:40:41,240
Looks like you have to go home

636
00:40:41,240 --> 00:40:42,640
and couldn't come along.

637
00:40:43,560 --> 00:40:44,320
It's OK.

638
00:40:44,880 --> 00:40:46,320
So we can catch up.

639
00:40:49,160 --> 00:40:51,480
Ms. Qu and Yanzhen are so close.

640
00:40:51,480 --> 00:40:52,840
Not as close as you two.

641
00:40:52,960 --> 00:40:54,320
You're his fiancée.

642
00:40:54,480 --> 00:40:55,880
His wife in the future.

643
00:40:56,000 --> 00:40:57,530
You're closer, naturally.

644
00:40:58,240 --> 00:40:58,720
Yanzhen,

645
00:40:58,720 --> 00:41:00,640
don't call her Miss Dong anymore.

646
00:41:00,640 --> 00:41:01,720
How detached it sounds!

647
00:41:01,720 --> 00:41:02,520
Family rules.

648
00:41:02,920 --> 00:41:03,850
We can't help it.

649
00:41:04,400 --> 00:41:05,400
Both our families

650
00:41:05,400 --> 00:41:07,660
are traditionally courteous families.

651
00:41:07,680 --> 00:41:10,140
Our ancestors all worked in the royal court.

652
00:41:10,200 --> 00:41:11,800
We have strict family rules.

653
00:41:11,920 --> 00:41:13,680
Though it's a different time,

654
00:41:14,200 --> 00:41:16,460
when new rules and ideas are introduced,

655
00:41:16,600 --> 00:41:18,480
we still have to stick to some family rules

656
00:41:18,480 --> 00:41:19,480
and courtesies.

657
00:41:20,240 --> 00:41:22,000
Yanzhen doesn't address me with my first name

658
00:41:22,000 --> 00:41:23,330
because he respects me.

659
00:41:24,240 --> 00:41:25,480
You have a point.

660
00:41:26,320 --> 00:41:27,720
Then you should call him Mr. Gu,

661
00:41:27,720 --> 00:41:29,580
instead of his first name, right?

662
00:41:34,880 --> 00:41:35,560
Qu Manting!

663
00:41:36,760 --> 00:41:37,600
Qu Manting!

664
00:41:38,080 --> 00:41:39,010
It's really you.

665
00:41:39,240 --> 00:41:40,680
I watched your movies.

666
00:41:40,920 --> 00:41:41,440
Really?

667
00:41:41,440 --> 00:41:42,640
You're so beautiful.

668
00:41:42,720 --> 00:41:43,360
Thanks.

669
00:41:43,880 --> 00:41:45,140
Can I have a signature?

670
00:41:45,720 --> 00:41:46,360
Of course.

671
00:41:57,120 --> 00:41:57,680
OK.

672
00:41:59,000 --> 00:41:59,680
Thank you.

673
00:41:59,920 --> 00:42:00,380
It's OK.

674
00:42:01,320 --> 00:42:01,920
Let's go.

675
00:42:04,920 --> 00:42:05,780
Sorry for that.

676
00:42:06,480 --> 00:42:08,240
Looks like you're very famous.

677
00:42:09,440 --> 00:42:10,640
I starred in a few movies.

678
00:42:10,640 --> 00:42:11,840
They get me some fame.

679
00:42:11,880 --> 00:42:12,960
Like you just said,

680
00:42:13,600 --> 00:42:16,730
some companies invite me to sing for them occasionally.

681
00:42:16,760 --> 00:42:17,760
But for women,

682
00:42:18,200 --> 00:42:20,160
it's too hard to make a living.

683
00:42:20,600 --> 00:42:22,560
Well, not as easy as your life.

684
00:42:22,880 --> 00:42:24,480
You grow up in a good family

685
00:42:24,480 --> 00:42:25,560
and live in dream.

686
00:42:26,760 --> 00:42:27,640
I told you

687
00:42:27,920 --> 00:42:28,960
not to work.

688
00:42:29,200 --> 00:42:30,200
It's hard for you.

689
00:42:30,280 --> 00:42:31,400
What can I do?

690
00:42:31,400 --> 00:42:32,360
You're getting married,

691
00:42:32,360 --> 00:42:33,440
and can't take care of me anymore.
